\fBsetItemMode()\fP, \fBitemMode()\fP, \fBQwtLegendItem::IdentifierMode\fP \fBQwtLegendItem::clicked()\fP, \fBQwtLegendItem::checked()\fP, \fBQwtPlot::legendClicked()\fP, \fBQwtPlot::legendChecked()\fP 
.RE
.PP

